breakWith.Hover:
### Description:
Skips all loop iterations and immediately returns the given value.


### Syntax:
breakWith return

### Parameters:
return: Anything - Value to be returned when iterations are skipped

### Return Value:
Anything


### Example 1:
This loop will stop once 
```sqf
_i
```
 reaches 5; the output will be "0", "1", "2", "3", "4" and finally "END".

```sqf
