###

continueWith.Hover:
### Description:
Skips the current loop iteration, continues with the next one and returns the given value.


### Syntax:
continueWith return

### Parameters:
return: Anything - Value to be returned when iteration is skipped

### Return Value:
Anything


### Example 1:
The result of this code will be 
```sqf
[2, "TEST", 4]
```
.

```sqf
[1, 2, 3] apply {
	if (_x == 2) then {
		continueWith "TEST";
	} else {
		_x + 1
	};
};
```



