intersect.Hover:
[Global argument]

### Description:
Finds named selections in object which are in specified LOD, intersected by given section of a line. Return value is in the form of [selection, distance]. Multiple returned arrays are nested within a single array. No intersection returns [].  could be one of the following: 



### Syntax:
[object, lodName] intersect [begPos, endPos]

### Parameters:
[object, lodName]: Array
object: Object
lodName: String
[begPos, endPos] : Array
begPos: Array - format PositionAGL
endPos: Array - format PositionAGL

### Return Value:
Array - array of intersections in format: [[selection, distance],...], where

The results are also sorted, closest selection first


### Example 1:

```sqf
